race.comment: CARTEL MODEL (2) is a promising type who notched his 15th career success when too good (19.34) at Bulli last time. Has a strong winning record at this journey. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Looks the one to beat. ORSON JIMMY (3) was last seen getting around 365m at this track in a sharp 20.70 for a 2.5 lengths success. Harder here but expected to measure up. JAKE PERALTA (8) was in the minor money with a slick 20.73, finishing second in a Mix 1/2/3 at this track last start. Expected to feature again. MARVEL ZOMBIE (1) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.
